<D>__{would you mind if i borrowed your computer console?}
<C>__{lime}
<D>__{what?}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{i will bring it back in ten minutes.}
<C>__{lime}
<D>__{you want to take my console into your office?}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{lime}
<P>__{(after a moment's consideration)}
<D>__{i will tell you what .... you tell me what and i will do it for. i'm a bit of a whizz on this thing.}
<P>__{(indicates computer console)}
<A>__{sam hesitates, but sees that there's no other way.}
<C>__{sam}
<P>__{(taking print out on jill from his pocket)}
<D>__{alright. there's someone i want to check out. a woman called gillian layton.}
