<D>__{you must be joking }
<P>__{(entirely unconvincing)}
<D>__{when there's a woman involved there's no stopping me. now, let me have that sheet.}
<A>__{he takes jill's print out sheet from sam and begins to punch the keys laboriously with one finger. nothing happens.}
